5 text-yellow-500\" />\r\n                    <span>в”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв•ӘШөв•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•ӘШІв•Әв•Ўв•ӘВ»в•Әв–’в”ҳГЁв”ҳВҶ</span>\r\n                  </CardTitle>\r\n                  <Link href=\"/leaderboard\">\r\n                    <Button variant=\"link\" size=\"sm\">\r\n                      в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГўв”ҳВ„\r\n                      <ArrowRight className=\"h-4 w-4 mr-1\" />\r\n                    </Button>\r\n                  </Link>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </CardHeader>\r\n              <CardContent className=\"space-y-3\">\r\n                {loading ? (\r\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-center py-8\">\r\n                    <div className=\"animate-spin rounded-full h-6 w-6 border-b-2 border-yellow-600\" />\r\n                  </div>\r\n                ) : (\r\n                  leaderboard.map((entry, index) => (\r\n                    <motion.div\r\n                      key={entry.rank}\r\n                      initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 10 }}\r\n                      animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\r\n                      transition={{ delay: index * 0.1 }}\r\n                      className={`flex items-center gap-4 p-3 rounded-xl transition-all ${\r\n                        entry.isCurrentUser \r\n                          ? \"bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-50 to-orange-50 border-2 border-yellow-300\" \r\n                          : \"bg-slate-50 hover:bg-slate-100\"\r\n                      }`}\r\n                    >\r\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white shadow-sm\">\r\n                        {getRankIcon(entry.rank)}\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div className=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\r\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\r\n                          <span className=\"font-bold text-sm text-slate-900\">\r\n                            {entry.badge} {entry.name}\r\n                          </span>\r\n                          {entry.isCurrentUser && (\r\n                            <Badge className=\"bg-yellow-600 text-white text-xs\">в•ӘШ«в”ҳВҶв•ӘШІ</Badge>\r\n                          )}\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mt-1\">\r\n                          <TrendingUp className=\"h-3 w-3 text-green-600\" />\r\n                          <span className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\r\n                            {formatScore(entry.score)} в”ҳВҶв”ҳГ©в•Әв•–в•ӘШұ\r\n                          </span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div className=\"text-lg font-bold text-slate-700\">\r\n                        #{entry.rank}\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </motion.div>\r\n                  ))\r\n                )}\r\n              </CardContent>\r\n            </Card>\r\n          </motion.div>\r\n\r\n          {/* Recent Achievements */}\r\n          <motion.div\r\n            initial={{ opacity: 0, x: 20 }}\r\n            whileInView={{ opacity: 1, x: 0 }}\r\n            viewport={{ once: true }}\r\n            transition={{ delay: 0.2 }}\r\n          >\r\n            <Card className=\"border-slate-200/80 shadow-lg h-full\">\r\n              <CardHeader>\r\n                <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\r\n                  <CardTitle className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\r\n                    <Award className=\"h-5 w-5 text-purple-500\" />\r\n                    <span>в•ӘШӯв”ҳВҶв•ӘШҙв•ӘШҜв•Әв–“в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШөв•ӘВ»в”ҳГЁв•ӘШів•ӘШұ</span>\r\n                  </CardTitle>\r\n                  <Link href=\"/achievements\">\r\n                    <Button variant=\"link\" size=\"sm\">\r\n                      в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГўв”ҳВ„\r\n                      <ArrowRight className=\"h-4 w-4 mr-1\" />\r\n                    </Button>\r\n                  </Link>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </CardHeader>\r\n              <CardContent className=\"space-y-4\">\r\n                {loading ? (\r\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-center py-8\">\r\n                    <div className=\"animate-spin rounded-full h-6 w-6 border-b-2 border-purple-600\" />\r\n                  </div>\r\n                ) : (\r\n                  recentAchievements.map((achievement, index) => (\r\n                    <motion.div\r\n                      key={achievement.id}\r\n                      initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 10 }}\r\n                      animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\r\n                      transition={{ delay: index * 0.1 }}\r\n                      className=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-pink-50 border border-purple-100 hover:shadow-md transition-all\"\r\n                    >\r\n                      <div className=\"flex-shrink-0 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 to-pink-600 p-3 text-white\">\r\n                        {achievement.icon}\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div className=\"flex-1 min-w-0\">\r\n                        <h3 className=\"font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1\">\r\n                          {achievement.title}\r\n                        </h3>\r\n                        <p className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-2\">\r\n                          {achievement.description}\r\n                        </p>\r\n                        {achievement.progress !== undefined && achievement.total && achievement.total > 0 && (\r\n                          <div className=\"mt-2\">\r\n                            <div className=\"flex justify-between text-xs mb-1\">\r\n                              <span className=\"text-muted-foreground\">в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв”ҳГ©в•ӘВ»в”ҳГ </span>\r\n                              <span className=\"font-semibold\">\r\n                                {achievement.progress} / {achievement.total}\r\n                              </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div className=\"h-2 bg-slate-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\r\n                              <motion.div\r\n                                initial={{ width: 0 }}\r\n                                animate={{ width: `${(achievement.progress / achievement.total) * 100}%` }}\r\n                                transition={{ duration: 0.8 }}\r\n                                className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 rounded-full\"\r\n                              />\r\n                            </div>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                        )}\r\n                        {achievement.unlockedAt && (\r\n                          <div className=\"mt-2 flex items-center gap-2\">\r\n                            <Share2 className=\"h-3 w-3 text-muted-foreground\" />\r\n                            <Button variant=\"link\" size=\"sm\" className=\"h-auto p-0 text-xs\">\r\n                              в•Әв”Өв•ӘШҜв•Әв–’в”ҳГў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШӯв”ҳВҶв•ӘШҙв•ӘШҜв•Әв–“\r\n                            </Button>\r\n                          </div>\r\n                        )}\r\n                      </div>\r\n                    </motion.div>\r\n                  ))\r\n                )}\r\n              </CardContent>\r\n            </Card>\r\n          </motion.div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        {/* Share Achievements CTA */}\r\n        <motion.div\r\n          initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}\r\n          whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\r\n          viewport={{ once: true }}\r\n          transition={{ delay: 0.4 }}\r\n          className=\"mt-8\"\r\n        >\r\n          <Card className=\"border-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-600 to-orange-600 shadow-xl\">\r\n            <CardContent className=\"p-6\">\r\n              <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between ga