 Allowed unused vars must match /^_/u.","line":104,"column":10,"nodeType":null,"messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":104,"endColumn":40}],"suppressedMessages":[],"errorCount":0,"fatalErrorCount":0,"warningCount":4,"fixableErrorCount":0,"fixableWarningCount":0,"source":"/**\r\n * в”ҳГ в•ӘШів•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„ в•ӘШҜв•Әв”Ӯв•ӘШІв•ӘВ«в•ӘВ»в•ӘШҜв”ҳГ  в•Әв”Ӯв•Әв–’в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Ј в”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳВ„в”ҳВҒв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•Әв•–в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ\r\n * Quick Usage Example for Header Enhancements\r\n */\r\nimport { logger } from '@/lib/logger';\r\n\r\n\r\n// ==================== в”ҳГ в•ӘШів•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„ 1: в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҙв”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Ј в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•Әв•–в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ ====================\r\nimport {\r\n\theaderEnhancements,\r\n\tgetEnhancementsByPriority,\r\n\tgetEnhancementsByCategory,\r\n\tgetEnhancementStats\r\n} from \"./header-enhancements\";\r\n\r\n// в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШөв•Әв•Ўв”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„ в•Әв•Јв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ« в•ӘШҙв”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Ј в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•Әв•–в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ\r\nlogger.info(\"в•ӘШӯв•ӘШҙв”ҳГ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГЁ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•Әв•–в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ:\", headerEnhancements.length);\r\n\r\n// в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШөв•Әв•Ўв”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„ в•Әв•Јв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ« в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•Әв•–в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•Әв•Јв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ в”ҳВҒв”ҳГ©в•Әв•–\r\nconst highPriorityFeatures = getEnhancementsByPriority(\"high\");\r\nlogger.info(\"в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•Әв•–в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•Әв•Јв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ:\", highPriorityFeatures.length);\r\n\r\n// в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШөв•Әв•Ўв”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„ в•Әв•Јв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ« в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•Әв•–в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в”ҳВҒв”ҳГЁ в”ҳВҒв•ӘШ®в•ӘШұ в”ҳГ в•Әв•Јв”ҳГЁв”ҳВҶв•ӘШұ\r\nconst searchFeatures = getEnhancementsByCategory(\"в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ°в•ӘШөв•ӘШі в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•ӘШІв”ҳГ©в•ӘВ»в”ҳГ \");\r\nlogger.info(\"в”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв–“в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ°в•ӘШөв•ӘШі:\", searchFeatures);\r\n\r\n// в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШөв•Әв•Ўв”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„ в•Әв•Јв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ« в•ӘШӯв•ӘШөв•Әв•Ўв•ӘШҜв•ӘШ®в”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ\r\nconst stats = getEnhancementStats();\r\nlogger.info(\"в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШӯв•ӘШөв•Әв•Ўв•ӘШҜв•ӘШ®в”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ:\", stats);\r\n\r\n// ==================== в”ҳГ в•ӘШів•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„ 2: в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘВ«в•Әв•–в•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв”ҳВҶв”ҳВҒв”ҳГЁв•Әв–‘ ====================\r\nimport {\r\n\timplementationPhases,\r\n\tpriorityImplementationOrder,\r\n\trecommendedTechnologies\r\n} from \"./header-implementation-plan\";\r\n\r\n// в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҙв”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Ј в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШөв”ҳВ„\r\nimplementationPhases.forEach((phase, index) => {\r\n\tlogger.info(`\\nв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•Әв–’в•ӘШөв”ҳВ„в•ӘШұ ${phase.phase}: ${phase.name}`);\r\n\tlogger.info(`в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•ӘВ»в•ӘШұ: ${phase.duration}`);\r\n\tlogger.info(`в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв–“в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ: ${phase.features.length} в”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв–“в•ӘШұ`);\r\n});\r\n\r\n// в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ\r\npriorityImplementationOrder.forEach((priority) => {\r\n\tlogger.info(`\\n${priority.level}:`);\r\n\tpriority.features.forEach((feature) => {\r\n\t\tlogger.info(`  - ${feature}`);\r\n\t});\r\n});\r\n\r\n// в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв”ҳГ©в”ҳВҶв”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳГӘв•Әв•Ўв”ҳГ« в•ӘШ°в”ҳГ§в•ӘШҜ\r\nlogger.info(\"\\nв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв”ҳГ©в”ҳВҶв”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳГӘв•Әв•Ўв”ҳГ« в•ӘШ°в”ҳГ§в•ӘШҜ в”ҳВ„в”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в•ӘВ»в•ӘШҜв•ӘШ©:\", recommendedTechnologies.performance);\r\nlogger.info(\"в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв”ҳГ©в”ҳВҶв”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳГӘв•Әв•Ўв”ҳГ« в•ӘШ°в”ҳГ§в•ӘШҜ в”ҳВ„в”ҳВ„в•ӘШ°в•ӘШөв•ӘШі:\", recommendedTechnologies.search);\r\n\r\n// ==================== в”ҳГ в•ӘШів•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„ 3: в•ӘШҜв•Әв”Ӯв•ӘШІв•ӘВ«в•ӘВ»в•ӘШҜв”ҳГ  в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳВ„в•ӘВ«в•Әв•Ў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•Әв”Ӯв•Әв–’в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Ј ====================\r\nimport {\r\n\theaderFeaturesSummary,\r\n\tquickStats,\r\n\tquickPriorities\r\n} from \"./header-features-summary\";\r\n\r\n// в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв–“в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШөв•Әв”Ӯв•ӘШ° в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳВҒв•ӘШ®в•ӘШұ\r\nObject.entries(headerFeaturesSummary).forEach(([category, features]) => {\r\n\tlogger.info(`\\n${category}:`);\r\n\tfeatures.forEach((feature) => {\r\n\t\tlogger.info(`  - ${feature}`);\r\n\t});\r\n});\r\n\r\n// в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШӯв•ӘШөв•Әв•Ўв•ӘШҜв•ӘШ®в”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•Әв”Ӯв•Әв–’в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Јв•ӘШұ\r\nlogger.info(\"\\nв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШӯв•ӘШөв•Әв•Ўв•ӘШҜв•ӘШ®в”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•Әв”Ӯв•Әв–’в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Јв•ӘШұ:\", quickStats);\r\n\r\n// в•Әв•Јв•Әв–’в•Әв•ў в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•Әв”Ӯв•Әв–’в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Јв•ӘШұ\r\nlogger.info(\"\\nв•ӘШ«в”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•Әв–’в•ӘШөв”ҳВ„в•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ«:\", quickPriorities.phase1);\r\n\r\n// ==================== в”ҳГ в•ӘШів•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„ 4: в•ӘШӯв”ҳВҶв•Әв”Өв•ӘШҜв•ӘШ© в”ҳГ©в•ӘШҜв•ӘШ®в”ҳГ в•ӘШұ в”ҳГ в”ҳГ§в•ӘШҜв”ҳГ  ====================\r\nfunction createTaskList() {\r\n\tconst highPriority = getEnhancementsByPriority(\"high\");\r\n\tconst simpleTasks = highPriority.filter((e) => e.complexity === \"simple\");\r\n\t\r\n\tlogger.info(\"\\nв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳГ§в•ӘШҜв”ҳГ  в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•Әв”Ӯв”ҳГ§в”ҳВ„в•ӘШұ в•Әв•Јв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ:\");\r\n\tsimpleTasks.forEach((task, index) => {\r\n\t\tlogger.info(`${index + 1}. ${task.feature} (${task.category})`);\r\n\t});\r\n\t\r\n\treturn simpleTasks.map((task) => ({\r\n\t\ttitle: task.feature,\r\n\t\tcategory: task.category,\r\n\t\tdescription: task.description\r\n\t}));\r\n}\r\n\r\n// ==================== в”ҳГ в•ӘШів•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„ 5: в•ӘШІв•Әв•Ўв”ҳВҒв”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ в•ӘШөв•Әв”Ӯв•ӘШ° в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•Әв•Јв•ӘШҜв”ҳГЁв”ҳГЁв•Әв–’ ====================\r\nfunction getRecommendedFeatures() {\r\n\t// в”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв–“в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в•Әв•Јв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в”ҳГӘв”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв”ҳГЁв•ӘШұ в”ҳГӘв•Әв”Ӯв”ҳГ§в”ҳВ„в•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв”ҳВҶв”ҳВҒв”ҳГЁв•Әв–‘\r\n\treturn headerEnhancements.filter(\r\n\t\t(e) => e.priority === \"high\" && e.complexity === \"simple\"\r\n\t);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// в”ҳГ в”ҳГЁв•Әв–“в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ в”ҳГ в•Әв•Јв”ҳГ©в•ӘВ»в•ӘШұ в”ҳВ„в”ҳГўв”ҳВҶ в”ҳГ в”ҳГ§в”ҳГ в•ӘШұ\r\nfunction getComplexHighPriorityFeatures() {\r\n\treturn headerEnhancements.filter(\r\n\t\t(e) => e.priority === \"high\" && e.complexity === \"complex\"\r\n\t);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// ==================== в”ҳГ в•ӘШів•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„ 6: в•ӘШӯв”ҳВҶв•Әв”Өв•ӘШҜв•ӘШ© в•ӘВ«в•Әв•–в•ӘШұ в•ӘШІв”ҳВҶв”ҳВҒв”ҳГЁв•Әв–‘ в”ҳГ в•ӘВ«в•Әв•Ўв•Әв•Ўв•ӘШұ ====================\r\nfunction createCustomImplementationPlan(focusAreas: string[]) {\r\n\tconst plan = focusAreas.map((area) => {\r\n\t\tconst features = getEnhancementsByCategory(area);\r\n\t\treturn {\r\n\t\t\tarea,\r\n\t\t\tfeatures: features.length,\r\n\t\t\thighPriority: features.filter((f) => f.priority === \"high\").length,\r\n\t\t\testimatedTime: `${features.length * 2} в•ӘШ«в•Әв”Ӯв•ӘШҜв•ӘШ°в”ҳГЁв•Әв•Ј`\r\n\t\t};\r\n\t});\r\n\t\r\n\treturn plan;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// в•ӘШҜв•Әв”Ӯв•ӘШІв•ӘВ«в•ӘВ»в•ӘШҜв”ҳГ  в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•ӘШів•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„\r\nconst customPlan = createCustomImplementationPlan([\r\n\t\"в•ӘШІв•ӘШҙв•Әв–’в•ӘШ°в•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•Әв”Ӯв•ӘШІв•ӘВ«в•ӘВ»в”ҳГ \",\r\n\t\"в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ°в•ӘШөв•ӘШі в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•ӘШІв”ҳГ©в•ӘВ»в”ҳГ \",\r\n\t\"в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в•ӘВ»в•ӘШҜв•ӘШ© в”ҳГӘв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•ӘШөв•Әв”Ӯв”ҳГЁв”ҳВҶв•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ\"\r\n]);\r\n\r\nlogger.info(\"\\nв•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘВ«в•Әв•–в•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в•ӘВ«в•Әв•Ўв•Әв•Ўв•ӘШұ:\", customPlan);\r\n\r\n","usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"D:\\thanawy\\src\\components\\header\\UserMenu.tsx","messages":[{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":1,"message":"'CreditCard' is defined but never used. Allowed unused vars must match /^_/u.","line":12,"column":3,"nodeType":null,"messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":12,"endColumn":13},{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":1,"message":"'cn' is defined but never used. Allowed unused vars must match /^_/u.","line":26,"column":10,"nodeType":null,"messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":26,"endColumn":12},{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":1,"message":"'motion' is defined but never used. Allowed unused vars must match /^_/u.","line":27,"column":10,"nodeType":null,"messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":27,"endColumn":16}],"suppressedMessages":[],"errorCount":0,"fatalErrorCount":0,"warningCount":3,"fixableErrorCount":0,"fixableWarningCount":0,"source":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React from \"react\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\nimport { \n  User, \n  Settings, \n  LayoutDashboard, \n  LogOut, \n  Bell, \n  Shield, \n  CreditCard \n} from \"lucide-react\";\nimport { useAuth } from \"@/contexts/auth-context\";\nimport {\n  DropdownMenu,\n  DropdownMenuContent,\n  DropdownMenuGroup,\n  DropdownMenuItem,\n  DropdownMenuLabel,\n  DropdownMenuSeparator,\n  DropdownMenuTrigger,\n} from \"@/components/ui/dropdown-menu\";\nimport { Avatar, AvatarFallback, AvatarImage } from \"@/components/ui/avatar\";\nimport { Button } from \"@/components/ui/button\";\nimport { cn } from \"@/lib/utils\";\nimport { motion } from \"framer-motion\";\n\nexport function UserMenu() {\n  const { user, logout } = useAuth();\n\n  if (!user) return null;\n\n  const initials = user.name \n    ? user.name.split(' ').map(n => n[0]).join('').toUpperCase()\n    : user.email[0].toUpperCase();\n\n  return (\n    <DropdownMenu>\n      <DropdownMenuTrigger asChild>\n        <Button \n          variant=\"ghost\" \n          className=\"relative h-10 w-10 rounded-full border-2 border-primary/10 p-0 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all overflow-hidden\"\n        >\n          <Avatar className=\"h-full w-full\">\n            <AvatarImage src={user.avatar || undefined} alt={user.name || user.email} />\n            <AvatarFallback className=\"bg-primary/5 text-primary font-bold\">\n              {initials}\n            </AvatarFallback>\n          </Avatar>\n          \n          {/* Online status indicator */}\n          <span className=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-green-500 ring-2 ring-background\" />\n        </Button>\n      </DropdownMenuTrigger>\n      \n      <DropdownMenuContent className=\"w-64\" align=\"end\" forceMount>\n        <DropdownMenuLabel className=\"font-normal\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col space-y-1 py-1\">\n            <p className=\"text-sm font-bold leading-none\">{user.name || user.username}</p>\n            <p className=\"text-xs leading-none text-muted-foreground\">\n              {user.email}\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </DropdownMenuLabel>\n        \n        <DropdownMenuSeparator />\n        \n        <DropdownMenuGroup>\n          <Link href=\"/dashboard\">\n            <DropdownMenuItem className=\"cursor-pointer gap-2 py-2\">\n              <LayoutDashboard className=\"h-4 w-4 text-primary\" />\n              <span>в”ҳВ„в”ҳГӘв•ӘШөв•ӘШұ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШІв•ӘШөв”ҳГўв”ҳГ </span>\n            </DropdownMenuItem>\n          </Link>\n          \n          <Link href=\"/profile\">\n            <DropdownMenuItem className=\"cursor-pointer gap-2 py-2\">\n              <User className=\"h-4 w-4 text-primary\" />\n              <span>в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в”ҳГ в”ҳВ„в”ҳВҒ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•Әв”Өв•ӘВ«в•Әв•Ўв”ҳГЁ</span>\n            </DropdownMenuItem>\n          </Link>\n          \n          <Link href=\"/settings\">\n            <DropdownMenuItem className=\"cursor-pointer gap-2 py-2\">\n              <Settings className=\"h-4 w-4 text-primary\" />\n              <span>в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШӯв•Әв•Јв•ӘВ»в•ӘШҜв•ӘВ»в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ</span>\n            </DropdownMenuItem>\n          </Link>\n        </DropdownMenuGroup>\n        \n        <DropdownMenuSeparator />\n        \n        <DropdownMenuGroup>\n          <DropdownMenuItem className=\"cursor-pointer gap-2 py-2\">\n            <Bell className=\"h-4 w-4 text-primary\" />\n            <span>в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШӯв•Әв”Өв•Әв•Јв•ӘШҜв•Әв–’в•ӘШҜв•ӘШІ</span>\n          </DropdownMenuItem>\n          \n          <DropdownMenuItem className=\"cursor-pointer gap-2 py-2\">\n            <Shield className=\"h-4 w-4 text-primary\" />\n            <span>в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘШ«в”ҳГ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВҶ</span>\n          </DropdownMenuItem>\n        </DropdownMenuGroup>\n        \n        <DropdownMenuSeparator />\n        \n        <DropdownMenuItem \n          className=\"cursor-pointer gap-2 py-2 text-destructive focus:bg-destructive/10 focus:text-destructive\"\n          onClick={() => logout()}\n        >\n          <LogOut className=\"h-4 w-4\" />\n          <span>в•ӘШІв•Әв”Ӯв•ӘШҙв”ҳГЁв”ҳВ„ в•ӘШҜв”ҳВ„в•ӘВ«в•Әв–’в”ҳГӘв•ӘШҙ</span>\n        </DropdownMenuItem>\n      </DropdownMenuContent>\n    </DropdownMenu>\n  );\n}\n","usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"D:\\thanawy\\src\\components\\header\\header-code-examples.ts","messages":[],"suppressedMessages":[],"errorCount":0,"fatalErrorCount":0,"warningCount":0,"fixableErrorCount":0,"fixableWarningCount":0,"usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"D:\\thanawy\\src\\components\\header\\header-enhancements.ts","messages":[],"suppressedMessages":[],"errorCount":0,"fatalErrorCount":0,"warningCount":0,"fixableErrorCount":0,"fixableWarningCount":0,"usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"D:\\thanawy\\src\\components\\header\\header-features-summary.ts","messages":[],"suppressedMessages":[],"errorCount":0,"fatalErrorCount":0,"warningCount":0,"fixableErrorCount":0,"fixableWarningCount":0,"usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"D:\\thanawy\\src\\components\\header\\header-implementation-plan.ts","messages":[],"suppressedMessages":[],"errorCount":0,"fatalErrorCount":0,"warningCount":0,"fixableErrorCount":0,"fixableWarningCount":0,"usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"D:\\thanawy\\src\\components\\header\\hooks\\index.ts","messages":[],"suppressedMessages":[],"errorCount":0,"fatalErrorCount":0,"warningCount":0,"fixableErrorCount":0,"fixableWarningCount":0,"usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"D:\\thanawy\\src\\components\\header\\hooks\\useFocusMode.ts","messages":[{"ruleId":"react-hooks/set-state-in-effect","severity":1,"message":"Error: Calling setState synchronously within an effect can trigger cascading renders\n\nEffects are intended to synchronize state between React and external systems such as manually updating the DOM, state management libraries, or other platform APIs. In general, the body of an effect should do one or both of the following:\n* Update external systems with the latest state from React.\n* Subscribe for updates from some external system, calling setState in a callback function when external state changes.\n\nCalling setState synchronously within an effect body causes cascading renders that can hurt performance, and is not recommended. (https://react.dev/learn/you-might-not-need-an-effect).\n\nD:\\thanawy\\src\\components\\header\\hooks\\useFocusMode.ts:48:9\n  46 |     // Load saved preferences\n  47 |     useEffect(() => {\n> 48 |         setMounted(true);\n     |         ^^^^^^^^^^ Avoid calling setState() directly within an effect\n  49 |         const saved = safeGetItem(STORAGE_KEY, { fallback: null });\n  50 |         if (saved && typeof saved === 'object' && saved !== null) {\n  51 |             setState((prev) => ({ ...prev, ...(saved as Partial<FocusModeState>) }));","line":48,"column":9,"nodeType":null,"endLine":48,"endColumn":19},{"ruleId":"react-hooks/set-state-in-effect","severity":1,"message":"Error: Calling setState synchronously within an effect can trigger cascading renders\n\nEffects are intended to synchronize state between React and external systems such as manually updating the DOM, state management libraries, or other platform APIs. In general, the body of an effect should do one or both of the following:\n* Update external systems with the latest state from React.\n* Subscribe for updates from some external system, calling setState in a callback function when external state changes.\n\nCalling setState synchronously within an effect body causes cascading renders that can hurt performance, and is not recommended. (https://react.dev/learn/you-might-not-need-an-effect).\n\nD:\\thanawy\